- **`transcript.json`** (47 KB) — 25 iterations conforming to `transcript_schema.json`, with self-contained, signed hypotheses naming actual columns and matched analyses (every analysis has `hypothesis_ids`, `effect_estimate`, `p_value`, `significant`).
